<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uz">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mening Mukammal Saytim</title>
    <style>
        /* BODY VA FON */
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .bg {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: url("sayt.jpg");
            background-size: cover; 
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            filter: blur(8px); 
            z-index: -1;
        }

        /* KONTENT */
        .content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
        }

        p {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        img {
            width: 300px;
            max-width: 80%;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #ff0055;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 10px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #ff66aa;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #00ccff;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 10px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #66e0ff;
        }

        /* RESPONSIVE */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            h1 { font-size: 32px; }
            p { font-size: 18px; }
            img { width: 80%; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- ORQA FON -->
    <div class="bg"></div>

    <!-- KONTENT -->
    <div class="content">
        <h1>E jigarim nima gap</h1>
        <p>Obuna bolib qoying qaytadiðŸ˜Ž</p>

